channel.title: I need some help with a Webclient.. Not a good coder at all :B
channel.description: I bet there are a milllion posts about webclients but I cant find a tutorial for a webclient WITH custom spirits. I could use a little help. I found a easy webclient, But I don't want it to stay basic, I want to add custom spirits for it. Its a html versioned one. Do I need to add the custom spirits or do I need a new one all together? I really like the webclient I am using and I hope that I don't have to change it. any help?
